wrapContent.value:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<EMEvent>
    <EMEvent>
        <eventName>Begin of process - ${camelId}</eventName>
        <eventType>START</eventType>
        <eventDescription>Replication process started</eventDescription>
        <eventAttributes>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>BTP-IS MessageId</name>
                <value>${header.SAP_MessageProcessingLogID}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Last Synch On</name>
                <value>${property.cbrLastSynchDateTime}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Cobrainer Job Architecture Id</name>
                <value>${property.cbrJobArchitecture}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Cobrainer Job Profile Type</name>
                <value>${property.cbrJobProfileType}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>SFSF Job Profile Sections</name>
                <value>${property.sfsfJobProfileSections}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total Cobrainer Job Profiles SELECTED</name>
                <value>${property.sumJobProf}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Job Profiles TO BE RESYNCHED</name>
                <value>${property.sumResynch}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Job Profiles TO BE CREATED</name>
                <value>${property.sumCreate}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Job Profiles TO BE ARCHIVED</name>
                <value>${property.sumArchive}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Job Profiles TO BE REACTIVATED</name>
                <value>${property.sumReactivate}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Skill Mapping TO BE CREATED</name>
                <value>${property.sumCreateMappingSkill}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Skill Mapping TO BE DELETED</name>
                <value>${property.sumDeleteMappingSkill}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Competency Mapping TO BE CREATED</name>
                <value>${property.sumCreateMappingComp}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Competency Mapping TO BE DELETED</name>
                <value>${property.sumDeleteMappingComp}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Job Profiles NOT SYNCHED</name>
                <value>${property.sumJobProfNotSync}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
        </eventAttributes>
    </EMEvent>
</EMEvent>
